# Paths excluded from `git archive` release tarballs (export-ignore).
#
# NOTE: the PRIMARY distribution channel is marketplace `git clone`, which
# export-ignore does NOT affect. For the clone channel, exclusion is enforced by
# the orphan release snapshot (see CLAUDE.md "Release boundary"), not this file.
# This file only trims the SECONDARY Zenodo `git archive` tarball.

# Contributor-facing docs — not needed in a downloaded archive
CLAUDE.md               export-ignore
CONTEXT.md              export-ignore

# Dev-only scaffolding / local config
docs/superpowers/       export-ignore
.claude/                export-ignore

# Tests — not needed by end users pulling a tarball
hooks/test/                             export-ignore
docs/references/test-index-resolve.js   export-ignore

# Line-ending normalization
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.svg text
